{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回\"救星\"讲述了柳若松在绝境中被神秘女子蓝蓝所救的故事。蓝蓝与青青看似亲热，实则互相暗算——青青以银针暗算蓝蓝，蓝蓝亦早有防备。蓝蓝向柳若松坦露，她救他是因为与青青是宿敌，青青帮丁鹏，她便要帮柳若松。蓝蓝甚至暗示可以嫁给他，条件是柳若松必须除掉妻子秦可情。柳若松休妻赶人，秦可情却用武当点穴手法反制。关键时刻，蓝蓝以松子暗器打断宋中手中利剑，救下柳若松。宋中在秦可情挑唆下欲杀柳若松，却反被蓝蓝制服。最终宋中刺杀秦可情后自刎殉情，揭示了他对秦可情的深情。蓝蓝安排柳若松在圆月山庄宴会上刺杀凌虚，以夺取武当掌门之位，并约定在会仙楼见面。全章充满权谋、背叛与生死抉择，展现了古龙笔下江湖的诡谲与人性的复杂。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "青青，青青，你知不知道我有多想你？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "蓝蓝，我也想死你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你真的想我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我当然想你，我简直想死你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我也想死你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我想你想得要命。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我也想你想得要命。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "好险。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "好险，若不是我也有准备，今天恐怕已死在她手里了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "现在我总算明白了，她说她想死你的时候，原来是想你死，她说想你想得要命的时候，原来是想要你的命。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你真聪明。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "可是我想不通，她的暗算既然已得手，为什么又忽然走了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "因为我在说想死她的时候，也是在想她死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "她的笑声又恢复了清悦：所以她给了我一针，我也给了她一下子，我想她受的罪绝不会比我轻，如果不赶快走，恐怕死得比我还快。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "现在你总该也已明白，我为什么要救你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "因为青青？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "一点也不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我平生只有一个对头，我的对头就是她，她要害你，我就要救你，她要帮丁鹏，我就要帮你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我一定替你争气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "就因为我看得出，你不管哪一点都不比丁鹏差，所以我才会选上你，就好像青青选上了丁鹏一样。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我不但可以救你，还可以替你做很多你连做梦都想不到的事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我甚至可以嫁给你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "如果不是因为你已经有了妻子，我一定会嫁给你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "丁鹏原来没有妻子，你只有这一点比不上他，除非……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "除非怎么样？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "除非你的妻子忽然死了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "她淡淡的接着道：每个人都要死的，早点死，晚点死，其实也没有什么太大的分别。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你说她反正是要走的，她是死是活，对你也没有什么分别。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "如果她已经走了，她是死是活，的确没有什么太大分别。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "可是她走了之后还会回来，既然她还是柳夫人，她要回来，随时都可以回来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "如果她已经不是柳夫人了呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "那么分别就很大了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我只希望你记住，你想要有什么样的收获，就得先付出什么样的代价。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你今天起来得真早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你想不想在这里再睡一会儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你走吧，用不着再等到明天，你现在就走吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "随便你到哪里去，随便你去干什么。以前我就不管你，以后我更不会管你了，从今以后你姓你的秦，我姓我的柳，我们互不相关，你也不必再回来了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "七出之条，你都已犯尽了，我不杀你，已经是你的运气，你还……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "他休了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "他不但休了我，而且还要把我赶出去。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "我嫁给他十几年，还不如别人家里养了十几年的狗，他要赶我走，我就得乖乖地滚蛋。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "那么我们就走吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你带我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "他不要你，我要你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你真的肯要我这个老太婆？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "就算你真的变成了个老太婆，我也绝不会变心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你真好，我果然没有看错你，只可惜……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "可惜什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "我还不想真的变成个老太婆，所以我每天要吃二十两银子一付的珍珠粉，免得我脸上起皱纹，我穿的衣服，都是从天竺和波斯运来的丝绸，好让别人看得年轻些，我每天要用羊奶洗澡，要好几个丫头侍候着我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你也应该知道，我是个吃惯了，穿惯了，花惯了的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "如果我嫁给了你，你能不能养得起我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我可以去做强盗来养你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你为什么要去做强盗？那又不是你的专长。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "杀人才是你的专长，你只要杀一个人，我们就可以过一辈子舒服日子了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你要我去杀谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你一挥手，我就变成了个可怜的寡妇了，不管丁鹏多凶恶，也绝不会来对付一个可怜的寡妇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好这个可怜的寡妇恰巧又是个很有钱的寡妇，不管谁能够娶到她，这一辈子都不必再发愁了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你为什么还不杀了她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "她要杀你，你就可以杀她，你不杀她，她就要杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这一定是吴道古铸成的，就算只剩下三寸长的一截，也可以杀得死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你的样子虽然凶狠，可是我知道你绝不会杀我的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "因为我比谁都了解你，你只会穿着八十两银子一件的袍子，喝着九十两银子一坛的好酒，抱着好看的女人，舒舒服服地坐在你那间屋里，叫别人去杀人，不管杀了多少人，你都绝不会难受的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "可是叫你自己手里拿着刀去杀人，你就不敢下手了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "他不敢，我敢。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你，你忍心下得了手？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你一定想不到我会杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "秦可情",
      "listener": "char_song_zhong",
      "text": "你……你为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "因为我早已想死了，你若不死，我怎么能死！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "宋中",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我平生杀人无算，只这一次杀得最痛快！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你已经付出了代价，我保证你一定会有收获的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "现在我已经有法子制她了，只要能制住青青，丁鹏根本不足为虑，只要你听我的话，好好地去做，我不但能帮你击败他们，不管你心里想做什么事，我都可以帮你做到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "武当派从来没有俗家弟子能做到掌门人的，可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你想做武当的掌门？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "可是现在希望最大的并不是我，是凌虚。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "区区一个武当掌门，算得了什么，你的志气也未免太小了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你知不知道上官金虹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "只要你愿意，我随时都能让你的成就超过上官金虹，超过小李飞刀，超过当今江湖中名气最大的谢晓峰……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你刚才说的凌虚，是不是天一道人的那个大徒弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "明天他也会在圆月山庄，说不定现在已经到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "他怎么会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "当然是丁鹏特地去请来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "其实你也应该明白，他为什么要特地去把凌虚请来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "想不到丁鹏做事竟忽然变得这么仔细。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "他明天晚上就会死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "他一向无病无痛，怎么会死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "因为有个人一剑刺穿了他的咽喉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "就是你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你若不敢，我也不勉强你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "反正现在我还没有嫁给你，你死了，我也不会太难受的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我不是不敢，我只怕……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "凌虚从小就开始练功夫，除了吃饭、念经、睡觉的时候之外，都在练功夫，我却还有很多别的事要做。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "也许我别的事做得太多了些，所以现在恐怕已经不是他的对手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你本来就不是他的对手，五十招之内，他就可以杀了你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 651
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "可是有我在，你还怕什么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "只要有我在你身旁，你十招之内，就可以杀了他……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "明天正午，我在城里的会仙楼等你，陪你一起去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你为什么要在城里等我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "因为我要你用轿子来接我，我要让别人知道，我是被你用轿子接走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我一定会准备一顶最大的轿子去接你，可是你……你为什么直到现在还不肯让我看看你的脸呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "明天你就会看见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "明天你到会仙楼，就会看见一个身上穿着身湖水蓝的衣裙，头上戴着枚百鸟朝风的珠花，脚上却穿着双红绣鞋的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "那个女人就是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    }
  ],
